-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This software incorporates components from the following projects:

Open Quantum Safe (liboqs)
  - License: MIT
  - https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs

DESILO FHE Library
  - License: BSD-3-Clause-Clear
  - https://fhe.desilo.dev/

The cryptographic algorithms implemented follow NIST standards:
  - FIPS 203: ML-KEM (Module-Lattice-Based Key-Encapsulation Mechanism)
  - FIPS 204: ML-DSA (Module-Lattice-Based Digital Signature Algorithm)
  - FIPS 205: SLH-DSA (Stateless Hash-Based Digital Signature Algorithm)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SECURITY NOTICE:

This software is provided for educational and research purposes. While it
implements standardized cryptographic algorithms, users should:

1. Conduct independent security audits before production deployment
2. Follow cryptographic key management best practices
3. Keep all dependencies updated to address security vulnerabilities
4. Consult with qualified security professionals for sensitive applications

The authors make no guarantees regarding the security or fitness of this
software for any particular purpose.
